;>;如果您正在寻找从旧款 AirPods 升级的好机会，那么一些 &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/21569881/black-friday-deals-start-time-hours-cyber-monday-stores&quot;>;黑色星期五早期促销&lt;/a>;现在正在进行，这正是您想要的。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-AirPods-3rd-Generation%2F5527780373%2F&amp;amp例如，;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;沃尔玛&lt;/a>;降低了一双 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/22744686/apple-airpods-third-gen-review&quot;>;&lt;strong>;Apple AirPods（第三代）&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a>;&lt;strong>;带 Lightning 充电盒&lt;/strong>;售价 94 美元，大幅折扣 75 美元，是我们迄今为止见过的最低价格。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;1N9SzO&quot;>;&lt;div data- anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如何在黑色星期五和网络星期一期间像专业人士一样购物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:// /www.theverge.com/21587765/black-friday-cyber-monday-best-deals-how-to-find&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;了解百思买、沃尔玛等的价格匹配政策&quot; ,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21570383/price-matching-policy-apple-google-microsoft&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 的 AirPods Pro 听力健康功能与听起来一样好&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24275178/apple-airpods-pro-hearing-aid-test-protection-preview&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/ div>; &lt;p id=&quot;ORNayq&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24245570/apple-airpods-4-review&quot;>;第四代 AirPods&lt;/a>; 现已上市 - 带有音频质量和舒适度略有改善，并且可以选择配备主动降噪功能和带有扬声器的无线充电盒，但第三代 AirPods 仍然能够满足日常音乐、播客、通话和其他聆听需求。充电盒为耳机增加了 24 小时的播放时间...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294504/apple-airpods-pro -third-gen-early-black-friday-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294504/apple-airpods-pro-third-gen-early-black-friday-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294504/apple-airpods-pro-third-gen-early-black-friday-deal-sale</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-12T09:56:29-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-12T09:56:29-05:00</updated><title>苹果收到欧盟警告，要求其结束“歧视性”地理封锁做法</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;欧盟星星中苹果标志的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/GiyWp5B8LgtCT4rPZMXN6BFxHuU=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73717703/STK450_EU_G.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;zun577&quot;>;欧盟在发现库比蒂诺公司的地理封锁措施可能违反欧盟规定后，指控苹果公司非法歧视欧盟客户。消费者保护规则。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;bPc0lc&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/detail/en/ip_24_5727&quot;>;周二通过新闻稿&lt;/a>;宣布，欧盟委员会和消费者保护合作组织 (CPC) 表示，一项联合调查发现，苹果公司对其 App Store、iTunes Store、Arcade 和 Books 实施了“几种可能被禁止的地理封锁做法”。播客和 Apple Music 服务。问题包括限制消费者使用其 Apple 帐户注册所在国家/地区发行的支付方式、阻止其他欧盟/欧洲经济区国家/地区提供的应用程序下载，以及针对特定地区的限制性...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294554/apple-eu-warning-geo-blocking-practices-app-store&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294554/apple-eu-warning-geo-blocking-practices-app-store" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294554/apple-eu-warning-geo-blocking-practices-app-store</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-12T09:20:24-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-12T09:20:24-05:00</updated><title> 23andMe 将结束其癌症研究计划并裁员 200 多人</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示 23andMe 标志的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hCEE3XbSuooO8qwxtX51rnrYGZA=/0x0:3744x2496/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads /chorus_image/image/73717649/1978235848.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Justin Sullivan/Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;GX5sIN&quot;>;23andMe 是 &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2024/11/11/2978617/0/en/23andMe-Announces-Business-Restructuring-to-Streamline-Operations-Reduc-Costs-and-Position-Company-for-the- Future.html&quot;>;解雇了 40% 的员工&lt;/a>;，即 200 多名员工，因为该公司试图从去年的大规模数据泄露事件中恢复过来，并扭转股价暴跌的局面。这家基因检测公司还宣布将关闭其治疗业务。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;IO4K3i&quot;>;尽管 23andMe 表示重组计划将花费约 1200 万美元，但预计将节省超过 3500 万美元。结果，同时“大幅”降低了运营费用。 23andMe 的治疗部门利用其遗传物质数据库研究了潜在的癌症治疗方法，该部门将结束所有临床试验，因为该公司考虑通过许可协议或资产出售来“最大化”该项目的价值。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;uiTUDB&quot; >;23andMe 过去的一年经历了动荡，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294473/23andme-layoffs-40-员工百分比&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294473/23andme-layoffs-40-percent-employees" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294473/23andme-layoffs-40-percent-employees</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-12T09:17:45-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-12T09:17:45-05:00</updated><title>智能睡眠是值得的</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一张手机控制床的照片，位于 Vergecast 背景之上。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/qnBMbU7Ndzn-fkUIo0fzdpAueJk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73717627/VST_1112_Site.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Alex Parkin / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;00Atoy&quot;>;每天晚上都能睡得更好，而且您无需做任何事情即可实现这一目标。听起来像是，&lt;em>;咳咳&lt;/em>;，梦想，对吧？听起来也像是凌晨 4 点当你无法入睡并且愿意尝试任何事情时，你可能会从电视广告推销员那里听到的一句话。事实证明，承诺是真的。它真的非常非常非常昂贵。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;v5WZGh&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://link.chtbl.com/vergecast&quot;>;&lt;em>;The Vergecast&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 的这一集，&lt;em>; >;The Verge&lt;/em>; 的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/authors/victoria-song&quot;>;Victoria Song&lt;/a>; 向我们讲述了她在睡眠设备方面的冒险经历。我们讨论了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24279552/eight-sleep-pod-4-ultra-review-tracking&#39;&quot;>;Eight Sleep Pod 4 Ultra&lt;/a>;，售价 4,700 美元的床垫需要订阅。如果您值得一夜好眠，那么这可能是值得的。我们还讨论了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/22/24275875/ozlo-sleepbuds-hands-on-bose-wearables-sleep-tracking&quot;>;Oura Ring 4&lt;/ a>;，整个&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.healthline.com/health-news/sleepmaxxing-tiktok-trend&quot;>;sleepmaxxing&lt;/a>;趋势，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/2024/10/22/24275875/ozlo-sleepbuds-hands-on-bose-wearables-sleep-tracking&quot;>;Ozlo Sleepbuds&lt;/a>; 以及其他方式...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294517/best-sleep-gadgets-eight-sleep-oura-spotify-ai-vergecast&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/ p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294517/best-sleep-gadgets-eight-sleep-oura-spotify-ai-vergecast" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294517/best-sleep-gadgets-eight-sleep-oura-spotify-ai-vergecast</id><author><name>大卫·皮尔斯</name></author></entry></feed>